Name: Asian Garden Mall
Description: A cultural hub of Vietnamese businesses and restaurants in the heart of Little Saigon.

Name: Vinpearl Water Park
Description: The first and only water park in Vietnam, providing a massive entertainment hub for indoor and outdoor activities, located at Phu Quoc Island in Nha Trang province.

Name: Antelope Canyon
Description: A awe-invoking slot canyon found in Northern Arizona, as a result of water erosion across sandstone for millions of years.

Name: Joshua Tree National Park
Description: A national park within California's Mojave and Colorado desert ecosystem that are reknown for the slow-growing Joshua Tree.

Name: San Francisco Painted Ladies
Description: A row of Victorian-style houses in San Francisco built from the late 19th century to the early 20th century, which survived the San Francisco earthquake of 1906.
